ARM: dts: stm32: add pwm cells to stm32mp157c

STM32 Timers support generic 3 cells PWM to encode PWM number, period and
polarity.

Fixes: 61fc211c484d ("ARM: dts: stm32: add timers support to stm32mp157c")

